{"tid":1640831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來緊急法實施後下個工作天(昨日)，已大量港幣換美元","createTime":"2019-10-09T06:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:00:36.000Z","uid":278765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8f58cf699272e4b0add0938e457749ce97b61c","tid":1640831,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"今日把握雞會，價極唔靚(7.86xx) 都將老本兑成美金，摟個客戶經理傾計。佢話單係昨日分行計已兑咗幾億港元。住宅區HSBC分行咋喎，幾億真係唔講得笑。<br />\n<br />\n信心危機，避險情緒。君子/小人都唔應該立於危場之下。齊阿哥大師話齋，亂世兩大目標: 保命+保本。<br />\n<br />\n如果皇帝不惜代價要香港舆柬莞/深圳/常平&hellip;&hellip;一體化，可能下一件要考慮嘅事係賣樓走人&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef9174d33cf50782f9df15898b9da94130ddb85","tid":1640831,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"c0764c768f0c817b57cd128fb0e62c4a16d4f97e","tid":1640831,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"分行計<br />\n即係分行有咁多美金cash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90f95a7a488da319e57d42940b42e931f5005ff","tid":1640831,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"早兩日我兌果陣都屌鬼<br />\n仆街上到7.86 , 聯繫匯率都係講緊7.85<br />\n唯有頂硬上"},{"pid":"e7b8ade93fa7132aa41dcc9ba3735f9c867e24b4","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"我琴日兌7.82咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee3b71a8dc9beb81d04d462fd4bd14b35040647","tid":1640831,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0764c768f0c817b57cd128fb0e62c4a16d4f97e","tid":1640831,"uid":25538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"分行計<br />\n即係分行有咁多美金cash <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"兑美金不等於兑美金現鈔啦<br />\n大數目啲嘅，可以Hkd 存款轉USD 存款，再遲啲轉離岸戶口。<br />\n<br />\n現在持大量現鈔保安風險好高㗎。就算屋企有閘萬都冇用。最高風險係來自，武景/老解扮港景，輕則擄人勒索，重則謀財害命，唔係冇可能的，反正冇任何刑責上身。"},{"pid":"1d0ca3d1fb8d0a7da9b3f16c06aad54139cc565e","tid":1640831,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b8ade93fa7132aa41dcc9ba3735f9c867e24b4","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"我琴日兌7.82咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:23:27.000Z","msg":"IB？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eead83022833fde24b2c215fea6f9c9a1e70ac3","tid":1640831,"uid":278765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d90f95a7a488da319e57d42940b42e931f5005ff","tid":1640831,"uid":61330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:43:47.000Z","msg":"早兩日我兌果陣都屌鬼<br />\n仆街上到7.86 , 聯繫匯率都係講緊7.85<br />\n唯有頂硬上"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"今日匯豐/恒生都係7.86xx！<br />\n如果早三四個星期，仍係7.85xx 走咪好囉。一心諗住林鄭個臭閪冇咁癲用緊急法，點知灰閪牛真係出現。"},{"pid":"df2d8e84e33bc692e578a8f267634917d13a4b82","tid":1640831,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b8ade93fa7132aa41dcc9ba3735f9c867e24b4","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"我琴日兌7.82咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"邊到兌呀"},{"pid":"5674d95e90a2265c3f301d17db84e1af946b3c7f","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2d8e84e33bc692e578a8f267634917d13a4b82","tid":1640831,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b8ade93fa7132aa41dcc9ba3735f9c867e24b4","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"我琴日兌7.82咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"邊到兌呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d506e070c3f6b9aac3211f0b8a37863788f982e4","tid":1640831,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5674d95e90a2265c3f301d17db84e1af946b3c7f","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df2d8e84e33bc692e578a8f267634917d13a4b82","tid":1640831,"uid":68231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7b8ade93fa7132aa41dcc9ba3735f9c867e24b4","tid":1640831,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:49:23.000Z","msg":"我琴日兌7.82咋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:57:16.000Z","msg":"邊到兌呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:36:37.000Z","msg":"重慶大廈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"